Table (ref) compares stage-2 classifiers, along with drill-down by the three predicates. The trends align with those observed in the books dataset, with {\em amp/pred g} achieving the highest scores. While performance is strong on the relatively easier CEO relation (ca. 65% R@P50), it struggles on the highly challenging hasSubsidiary relation.